        x -= 1.
        return x

        norm = FactorNormalization(mean=mean, std=std)
        norm(x)
        return x

            x = np.transpose(x, (0, 3, 1, 2)) if x.ndim == 4 else np.transpose(x, (2, 0, 1))
        x = x[:, ::-1, ...] if data_format == 'channels_first' else x[..., ::-1]
